OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,FThe Green Party's UK leader has warned
OL,8,Fmembers in Wales not to become
OL,9,Fcomplacent after polls predicted the
OL,10,Fparty will win its first ever seats in
OL,11,Fthe 2026 Senedd Election.
OL,13,FZack Polanski joined Wales leader
OL,14,FAnthony Slaughter on a visit to south
OL,15,FWales on Saturday for their final
OL,16,Fweekend of campaigning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,FITV Cymru Wales' most recent poll
OL,8,Fsuggested the Wales Green Party could
OL,9,Fgain seven seats in Thursday's
OL,10,Felection - a slight drop on the
OL,11,Fprevious poll.
OL,13,FSpeaking at a campaign event, Mr
OL,14,FPolanski said: "I'm really excited to
OL,15,Fsee those results roll in. I also know
OL,16,Fthough that there is a danger that if
OL,17,Fwe assume those results are brilliant,
OL,18,For we allow a moment of complacency to
OL,19,Fcome in, nothing is written yet.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,F"People might go, 'are you just
OL,8,Fmanaging expectations?', sure there's
OL,9,Fsome of that - we need to make sure
OL,10,Fthat we get at least one Senedd
OL,11,Fmember, that is a huge breakthrough -
OL,12,Flet's also make sure we maximise the
OL,13,Fvote across the whole of Wales.
OL,15,F"My point is we need to keep working
OL,16,Ffor it."
OL,18,FAnthony Slaughter denied being worried
OL,19,Fabout left-leaning voters losing their
OL,20,Fnerve and opting for a larger party at
OL,21,Fthe polls.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,F"I don't see left-leaning voters going
OL,8,Ffor Labour, just going by when you
OL,9,Fknock on doors and ask people how they
OL,10,Fvoted in the General Election and they
OL,11,Fsay Labour, I always wait a second and
OL,12,Fthen ask 'how's that going?', and some
OL,13,Fof the answers are quite spicy,
OL,14,Fthere's a general dissatisfaction.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,F"The more people get to understand the
OL,8,Fvoting system, that it is
OL,9,Fproportional, that if you vote green,
OL,10,Fyou will get Greens elected to the
OL,11,FSenedd, and in many cases that sixth
OL,12,Fseat the polls show is between Greens
OL,13,Fand Reform, I think when people
OL,14,Frealise that and realise that no
OL,15,Fparty's going to have an overall
OL,16,Fmajority, they like the idea of the
OL,17,FGreens being there holding the next
OL,18,Fgovernment to account."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
