PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,FBut his UK counterpart has come under
OL,8,Ffire this week after sharing an X post
OL,9,Fcondemning the police response to the
OL,10,FGolders Green attack.
OL,12,FZack Polanski has since apologised for
OL,13,Fsharing the post, which accused
OL,14,Fofficers of violently kicking the
OL,15,Fstabbing suspect in the head after he
OL,16,Fhad already been incapacitated.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1777896669
OL,3,CWales Greens urged not to be
OL,4,Ccomplacent by UK leader after poll
OL,5,Csuccess
OL,7,FMr Slaughter later said during an LBC
OL,8,Fdebate that the post seemed
OL,9,F"inappropriate", but speaking to ITV
OL,10,FCymru Wales on Saturday insisted the
OL,11,Fincident is "done and dusted".
OL,13,F"I don't think Zack will damage our
OL,14,Fchances here.
OL,16,F"Zack brings so much to these events,
OL,17,Fhe's inspiring so many people, his
OL,18,Fmessage of hope and boldness, he's
OL,19,Fbeen supporting us and working with us
OL,20,Fin Wales for many, many years now.
OL,21,FHe's always welcome here."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
